snippet.title: Roxy Raccoon's Pinball Panic - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
The second game in Sinomod Studio's Roxy Raccoon series, this time it's a pinball game with an actual story mode. For this footage, you will be seeing two tables to give you an idea on this game. The game also has 10 DLC, each with their own gimmicks and achievements. 🦝🦝🦝🦝🦝🦝🦝

Roxy Raccoon series, Roxy Raccoon's Pinball Panic (C) Sinomod Studio
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1807690/Roxy_Raccoons_Pinball_Panic/
